 Famine looked at the prog of the virus. Impressive they managed to hold it 
back. But it had broken free and had entered the spark. Even if they could 
stop it Famine had a secret back up. It was insurance policy but he doubted 
he would need to use it. He smiled as Apocalypse talked of dark mouse's 
healing power. Yes it seemed her protection would be a certanity.
